title: "We're devastated over the loss of life," says ZombiCon organizer.
text:
"We're devastated over the loss of life," says ZombiCon organizer. 
Published By: News-press.com - Today 
"I'm heartbroken," said Angeli Chin, spokesperson for Zombicon, from the event's headquarters on Sunday in Fort Myers. One person was killed...
